{"tid":762842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"邊隊英超隊最肯用青訓？","createTime":"2018-07-31T15:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T02:43:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"972da3d99091be40fe350c0108a61d08c7d4b040","tid":762842,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/8/728/22349098728/22357163279_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F8%2F728%2F22349098728%2F22357163279_600x399.jpg&h=49fbf7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=gOsAYTbq7bKlfZoPZX1Vdo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=579cf30b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】眾所周知，英格蘭代表隊目前靠熱刺撐起，但其實英超最肯用青訓小將的球會卻是阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n事實是，今時今日所指的青訓球員（Homegrown player），已不一定是本土小將。<br />\n<br />\n英國《倫敦晚報》統計指，前任雲加給後來者留下了寶貴的資產，上季青訓球員披甲時間達到7922分鐘，冠絕整個英超，當中包括伊禾比（Alex Iwobi）、韋舒亞、比利連等球員。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，2016/17球季嶄露頭角的土炮美蘭尼爾斯，上季披甲993分鐘，深受雲加器重，希望新帥艾美利接手後，這名小將仍獲機會。<br />\n<br />\n排名第2、3位分別是曼聯和愛華頓，熱刺三甲不入。有趣的是，紅魔上季派出過10青訓球員落場，但總上陣時間不多，最終上位是防守中場麥湯米尼，披甲694分鐘，與保羅普巴、拉舒福特和連格成為僅有主力。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"bb2484ba45ae212676840853c2932f36a34e0389","tid":762842,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"雲加的遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e25e1cdd50ddb1279ddc974ef66c4d1d19b1112","tid":762842,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091cc4f213364b29b41e0d65b6844ae37a513abe","tid":762842,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb507544c856dea8c6b9667